    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/smooth-spine/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=535239472514598116&sectionId=535641030012175148)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1rnfLJhur_text","label":"gg1rnfLJhur_text","default":"<p>Remember, There Is No Risk</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUIiS6Nzqo_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggUIiS6Nzqo_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-3e52e5da-f0a0-4aa2-b377-162b1c2e5e4a.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggg07mGkAIZ_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggg07mGkAIZ_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-e974317a-7a57-40f5-9d77-5860a4e46fe8.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggL5hrftsuY_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggL5hrftsuY_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-36ce5f4d-82f4-40b9-a6d9-707a8651ad51.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gghg5VAXcp0_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gghg5VAXcp0_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-6b4b77af-3d71-4f5a-adc6-930575b02c4e.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYCOMBExBB_text","label":"ggYCOMBExBB_text","default":"<p>The only risk you might encounter…</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gga0trqUolR_text","label":"gga0trqUolR_text","default":"<p>Is the pain and regret of missing the opportunity to get your SmoothSpine Pillow at this huge discount.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghIobo4EKw_text","label":"gghIobo4EKw_text","default":"<p>Sadly, I know exactly what will happen if you decide to pass up this opportunity. I’ve seen it happen so many times with other patients.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-U601IzHG_text","label":"gg-U601IzHG_text","default":"<p>And believe me, it’s NOT good.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVrV-GhfxV_text","label":"ggVrV-GhfxV_text","default":"<p>You’ll continue to waste time on painkillers, massages, exercises and other short-term fixes that don’t address the root cause of the issue.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkus78BYAX_text","label":"ggkus78BYAX_text","default":"<p>You might feel some temporary relief from time to time…</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6FJSM6X-z_text","label":"gg6FJSM6X-z_text","default":"<p>And maybe you’ll even trick yourself into accepting this as a way of life…</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCOKRy2iCy_text","label":"ggCOKRy2iCy_text","default":"<p>But deep down, you know the pain and discomfort will only get worse.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvioZBbyd-_text","label":"ggvioZBbyd-_text","default":"<p>I’m not saying this to SCARE you. I’m just trying to WARN you.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHB9nnce-3_text","label":"ggHB9nnce-3_text","default":"<p>Because if it’s ignored, it can lead to a far more serious problem.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJqiZUSwRX_text","label":"ggJqiZUSwRX_text","default":"<p>That’s why the choice you make today will be one of the most important decisions of your life. So… what will it be?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg60T5fsk29_text","label":"gg60T5fsk29_text","default":"<p>Are you going to turn down this opportunity and gamble with your chances?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKk_M4u6ta_text","label":"ggKk_M4u6ta_text","default":"<p>Or will you make the right choice… Order one, two, or three SmoothSpine Pillows…and spend the next few weeks working towards recovery fueled by great nights of sleep?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLeDkTG4BX_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggLeDkTG4BX_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-92d3992c-818c-4740-930b-eff40a9f95f7.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4pveXgNG3_text","label":"gg4pveXgNG3_text","default":"<p>Keep in mind… This isn’t just about you.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeqETREyoa_text","label":"ggeqETREyoa_text","default":"<p>This is about your family - who will always be worried about you losing your mobility by not trying to get better.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXv4ahagGg_text","label":"ggXv4ahagGg_text","default":"<p>This is about your grandkids - who will never get the chance to play with you because your pain keeps holding you back.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXcrHT4P0w_text","label":"ggXcrHT4P0w_text","default":"<p>This is about your partner - who will have to deal with living alone because you’ll just be a shell of yourself.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3wnpCu9SJ_text","label":"gg3wnpCu9SJ_text","default":"<p>You owe it to both yourself and your loved ones to give this a try.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYt_clPDXa_childItem_0","label":"ggYt_clPDXa_childItem_0","default":"<p>You can turn things around.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYt_clPDXa_childItem_1","label":"ggYt_clPDXa_childItem_1","default":"<p>You can get the relief that you've been looking for.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYt_clPDXa_childItem_2","label":"ggYt_clPDXa_childItem_2","default":"<p>You can get your old life back and enjoy the rest of your life.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggb71KBEHFp_text","label":"ggb71KBEHFp_text","default":"<p>Many of my patients have already made it happen. You can too.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZkgpmi5ut_text","label":"ggZkgpmi5ut_text","default":"<p>All you need is a little help from the best pain relief pillow that I know of - our <a href=\"https://smoothspine.com/products/pres-alp\"><span style=\"color:#0056B3;\"><strong><u>SmoothSpine Alignment Pillow</u></strong></span></a>.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglbhyK2ssY_text","label":"gglbhyK2ssY_text","default":"<p>So without further ado…</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXb-LHPOx7_text","label":"ggXb-LHPOx7_text","default":"<p>If you’re ready to do the right thing…</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcHZKPZgXm_text","label":"ggcHZKPZgXm_text","default":"<p>Hit the big green button below to secure your SmoothSpine Pillow</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcs9GiKDXp_text","label":"ggcs9GiKDXp_text","default":"<p>And keep in mind - If it doesn’t meet your expectations in any way, you get your money back</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdLkm9zYPw_label","label":"ggdLkm9zYPw_label","default":"<p>GET 50% OFF SmoothSpine™️<br>Alignment Pillow Now!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_Tzdd143l_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg_Tzdd143l_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-c8b219e2-0c8c-4291-b5ae-20c0bb542090.gif"},{"type":"html","id":"ggB7-SMAENe_text","label":"ggB7-SMAENe_text","default":"<p>UPDATE:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghFBF1MG0K_customText","label":"gghFBF1MG0K_customText","default":"As of"},{"type":"html","id":"gguhKZW9LR6_text","label":"gguhKZW9LR6_text","default":"<p>The demand for SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow has surged, and our inventory is flying off the shelves. Order your own for <span style=\"color:#D63837;\"><strong>50% OFF + FAST SHIPPING</strong></span> before it's too late.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggb_NTBCQHw_text","label":"ggb_NTBCQHw_text","default":"<p>Lock in your order while you can to get&nbsp; <strong>50% OFF + FAST SHIPPING</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggktsc4KGSR_text","label":"ggktsc4KGSR_text","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#D63837;\"><strong>NOTE:</strong></span> This deal is NOT available on Amazon or eBay.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggomCur9mPC_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggomCur9mPC_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-7aeea1d2-6ebb-40ab-9162-38cc8d7f34d0.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYZUG9F1ef_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggYZUG9F1ef_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.sh